      <title>渣打银行首席执行官温特斯谈回购、股价和增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-30/stanchart-ceo-winters-on-buybacks-share-price-growth-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[渣打银行首席执行官比尔·温特斯在彭博电视台讨论了该行数十亿美元的股票回购计划，与此同时，该银行报告称，受财富业务的推动，税前利润有所上升。“我们的经营环境有些困难，我认为我们需要了解渣打银行的差异化程度，”温特斯告诉丽兹·伯登。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-30/stanchart-ceo-winters-on-buybacks-share-price-growth-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 06:22:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>嘉能可将于下周宣布煤炭开采业务的未来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/glencore-to-announce-future-of-coal-mining-business-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[嘉能可公司 (Glencore Plc) 表示，在本月初完成对泰克资源有限公司 (Teck Resources Ltd.) 煤矿的收购后，将于下周在业绩发布会上宣布是否计划剥离煤炭业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/glencore-to-announce-future-of-coal-mining-business-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 06:20:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
