    <item>
      <title>大宗商品因中国市场动荡而抹去今年的涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/commodities-erase-year-s-gains-as-china-outlook-rattles-complex</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国经济前景不乐观、美国天然气价格下跌以及食品价格下跌，大宗商品今年的涨幅已全部回吐，原材料价格也因此承压。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/commodities-erase-year-s-gains-as-china-outlook-rattles-complex</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 03:49:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
